Saving your worldfrom boring food








Gabby Q.
                        
Research Chef


What excites him about BBQ and R&D?








Gabby Q.
Research Chef
Gabby possesses a sheer love of flavor. Anyone who’s tasted his grilled bone-in rib eye will attest to that. But it’s how he expertly combines that passion with a desire to delve into the “why” of flavor that makes him a standout culinary professional. As Lead Chef for our Simply Asia Foods brand and Research Chef for our key industrial partners, he creates highly innovative flavor solutions and contributes greatly to McCormick’s success.
Learn About Our Flavors and Brands








Saving your worldfrom boring food








Sindhu L.
Director, Financial Planning and Analysis


She knows where global forecasting and strategic insight meet.








Sindhu L.
Director, Financial Planning and Analysis
Sindhu’s role as Director of Financial Planning and Analysis puts her in touch with McCormick divisions all over the world. She supports our leadership with real insight that comes from a thorough knowledge of how each Business Unit works. Sindhu’s current position is enriched by many years working with our consumer business units and sales teams. It’s helping her make tough business decisions while being sensitive to globally diverse customs.
How We Research and Develop








Saving your worldfrom boring food








Amy W.
International Trade Compliance Specialist


How does she help us translate imported food products into meals to remember?








Amy W.
International Trade Compliance Specialist
Amy’s well-earned expertise in the complexities of import and export compliance, global commerce and international partnerships add up to a simple fact: No matter what the occasion, people want to experience meals they’ll remember. That’s why she complements her U.S. Customs and Border Protection assessments and foreign trade zone evaluations with leisure travel that includes plenty of culinary adventures. McCormick has recognized Amy for everything she brings to the table with the C.P. McCormick Gold and Sapphire Awards, and as an Emeritus Member of our Multiple Management Board and Accelerated Leadership program.
Learn More About Our Company









