McCormick & Co., Inc.

18 Loveton Circle 
Sparks MD 21152 United States
Phone: +1 410-___-____
Fax: +1 410-___-____
http://www.mccormick.com





167
Managers




250
IT employees




$194.7MEST.
IT Budget




McCormick is the world's largest spice maker and employs about 8,000 people. The company sells to retailers, food makers, food processors and restaurants. The company's global headquarters are located at Sparks, MD.
IT Structure •The IT department of McCormick & Co. is located at the company's Sparks, MD headquarters. 
•Global Strategy and worldwide IT Operations are supported by various divisions within the IT department.
•The Business Solutions Group, which is not directly under IT,… MoreIT Structure •The IT department of McCormick & Co. is located at the company's Sparks, MD headquarters. 
•Global Strategy and worldwide IT Operations are supported by various divisions within the IT department.
•The Business Solutions Group, which is not directly under IT, works closely with the department to achieve enterprise-wide goals. Other divisions, or "threads," under Business Solutions which rely heavily on the IT department are eCommerce and Electronic Data Exchange.

IT Intelligence Snippets
2012:
•McCormick has standardized its entire SAP environment on Tidal Software, a provider of application scheduling and performance management.
•The company recently completed the process of virtualizing floor HMI servers with VMware, as well as upgraded their Windows systems from XP to Windows 7.





