 Recipes Products Prep Guide Grilling Tips Brands McCormick Gourmet Lawry's Zatarain's Español Menu   Saved  Login   Search Sign up to save your favorite flavors.Sign up with FacebookSign up with emailProfileLogout   Search     Grilling Tips  We know our stuff when it comes to grilling. And with a few tricks, videos and recipes, you, too, will be master of the flame. Bring on the heat below. 
Know Your Heat 
Better flame leads to better flavor. Whether you’re a fan of gas, charcoal, open-flame or smokers, this is the info you need to get your grilling done right.
View Tips to Get the Heat Right  
Grilling Steak
From selecting the perfect cut to adding serious Grill Mates® flavor, check out our tips, techniques and videos to create the ultimate grilled steaks.
View Grilling Steak  
Grilling Chicken
Chicken will never be boring again. Explore epic marinades and rubs to ramp up flavor at the grill. Or experiment with trending grilling techniques … beer can chicken anyone?
View Grilling Chicken  
Grilling Veggies
The savory sidekick to juicy steaks and perfectly charred chicken? Grilled veggie sides (or main dishes) flavored with our epic marinades, seasonings and rubs.
View Grilling Veggies  
Grilling Seafood
Move over stove. Throw today’s catch directly to the grill for bold, smoky flavor. Surf and turf. Fish tacos. BBQ salmon. We’ve got everything you need for quick-grilled, mouth-watering meals.
View Grilling Seafood  

Grilling Pork
All you need: flame, flavor and the perfect cut of meat. Read on for our griller-knows-best tips and tricks to servin’ up juicy, seared, unforgettable pork. 
View Grilling Pork 
  
Build-Your-Own Burger (And More) Bar
From classic toppers to adventurous condiments and sauces, nothin’ says summer like a DYI burger, hot dog and sausage bar. 
View DIY Burger, Hot Dog & Sausage Bars

